  <brief_title>Dose Ranging Study With the Probiotic Combination (VSL#3) in Diarrhea IBS</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Multi-center, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled, Dose Ranging Study With VSL#3 in Diarrhea Predominant IBS Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center</agency>
