    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effects of VSL#3 on symptoms associated with diarrhea predominant IBS
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study will evaluate 2 doses of VSL#3 and placebo over a 4 week period in patients
      presenting with diarrhea predominant IBS symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
